              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/New_York"
            },
            "body": "Hi [~Naganarasimha Garla], it is worth for keeping the application if it is running. But problem is currently YARN does not identifies the reasons for the not progressing. App not progressing could be because of several reasons. So I feel, if any mechanism to get reason for not progressing applications, this could be handled. I believe, YARN-4091 is one such issue which trying to get more debug information and  planning to expose REST interface for getting per application progress information.",
